<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583>
    bibo:endPage "14" ;
    bibo:journal "Subterranean Biology" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "35" ;
    dc:creator "Garcia, Rafael; Andujar, Carmelo; Oromi, Pedro; Lopez, Heriberto" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Oromia orahan (Curculionidae, Molytinae), a new subterranean species for the Canarian underground biodiversity" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure4> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Habitus of Oromia orahan sp. nov. (female) in dorsal and lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/421043" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Structures of the male and female genitalia of Oromia orahan sp. nov. A aedeagus in dorsal and lateral view B spiculum gastrale C tegmen D spiculum ventrale E ovipositor. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-C), 0.8 mm (D), 0.03 mm (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/421044" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Appearance of mud / dirt covered (A) and clean (B) individuals of Oromia orahan sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/421045" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/subtbiol.35.52583.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Structures of Oromia orahan sp. nov. (letters without asterisks) and O. aguiari (letters with asterisks) A pronotum B aedeagus C spiculum ventrale D tegmen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/421046" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

